name: Beetlejuice Handbook for the recently deceased journal book notebook wallet holder
description:
How awesome is this?? I love the way it came out
Its great because it is a binder style, whereas you can simple open the clips and replace the pages as needed. on the front there is slots for cards, paper or whatever you wish to put in it and on the back inside cover there is a pocket maybe for photos, $100 bills (hehe), or maybe your notes on resurrecting the dead? Also there is a holder for a pen (pen not included)

You can use as a journal, notebook, sketchbook, calendar, etc
It comes with blank ruled pages and a 2013 / 2014 Calendar
appx 7.5" x 5.5" (insert pages size: 3.75" x 6.75")

magnetic flap closure


This would make a GREAT gift for the beetlejuice fan (why not treat yourself)

Book is faux suede and soft PU leather.
Front cover is where i applied the image - it is polyester fabric.
The image is heat set / printed right onto the fabric - it is not a decal - you cannot feel it.

Any questions please do not hesitate to ask
